.RS 4
Store plaintext passwords where account have \*(Aqstore passwords with reversible encryption\*(Aq set (on | off | default)\&. Default is \*(Aqoff\*(Aq
.RE
.PP
\-\-history\-length=HISTORY_LENGTH
.RS 4
The password history length (\fIinteger\fR
| default)\&. Default is 24\&.
