\-\-account\-lockout\-duration=ACCOUNT_LOCKOUT_DURATION
.RS 4
The length of time an account is locked out after exceeding the limit on bad password attempts (\fInumber of minutes\fR
| default)\&. Default is 30 mins\&.
.RE
